query:
SELECT
                COALESCE(
                    CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN stability > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) /
                    NULLIF(CAST(COUNT(*) AS REAL), 0.0) * 100.0,
                    0.0
                ) as "rate!: f64"
            FROM flashcards
            WHERE text_id = ?
